Step 1: Launch robot in gazebo

(new terminal)

If assessment_world is loaded in gazebo then use 

  roslaunch bot_nav gazebo.launch

Else use

  roslaunch bot_nav gazebo_empty_world.launch
  


Step 2: Launch amcl_demo

(new terminal)
roslaunch bot_nav amcl_demo.launch

Step 3: Launch Rviz

(new terminal)
roslaunch bot_nav rviz_amcl.launch



Refer ReadMe_teleop for manual control when required ("for gate control and ball allingment")


